graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Controller]

        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Architecture"
        direction TB
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Java Runtime<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, 8080/TCP internal]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>HTTP→gRPC<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Sidecar]
        ModelRuntime[Model Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe<br/>8001/TCP gRPC]
        StoragePuller[Storage Helper<br/>Init/Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes via| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|executes on| ModelRuntime
        StoragePuller -->|loads models for| ModelRuntime
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR]
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>legacy]

    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Runtime Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>8033/TCP, 8008/TCP]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitor]

    Deployment -->|contains| ModelMesh
    Deployment -->|contains| RESTProxy
    Deployment -->|contains| RuntimeAdapter
    Deployment -->|contains| ModelRuntime
    Deployment -->|contains| StoragePuller

    Controller -->|depends on| ETCD[ETCD v3.5.9<br/>2379/TCP]
    ModelMesh -->|stores metadata in| ETCD
    Controller -->|optionally uses| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS certs]
    StoragePuller -->|retrieves from| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    StoragePuller -->|reads from| PVC[PVC Storage]

    Controller -->|integrates with| KServe[KServe<br/>Shared CRD Schema]
    Controller -->|optionally uses| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ETCD fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
